The '''''Menagerie''''' was once a smuggler ship which was acquired by [[Kelly Vermillion]] in the [[Spice/Legends|spice]] mines of [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]]. Originally named '''''Long Shot''''', Vermillion and his gang renamed it in honor of their group of misfit aliens.

